Explain every line functionality for me in details

```text
shopt -s histappend        # append instead of overwrite
shopt -s cmdhist           # multiline commands stay together
shopt -s lithist           # preserve newlines
HISTSIZE=50000
HISTFILESIZE=100000
HISTCONTROL=ignoreboth    # ignore duplicates + leading space
```

---

How to work with this bindings?

```text
set -o vi
bind -m vi-command '"/": history-incremental-search-backward'
bind -m vi-command '"?": history-incremental-search-forward'
```

